data.description: Offering the BEST-PRICED HOME in all of River Hall, this nearly 2,600 sq ft, 2-story Lennar gem comes with a 2-YEAR HOME WARRANTY and boasts 4 BIG Bedrooms PLUS A DEN, 3 baths. Situated in GOLFER'S PARADISE, River Hall, known for its FUN and scenic GOLF COURSE, you'll appreciate the LOW HOA that covers CABLE and INTERNET. The OPEN-CONCEPT kitchen, filled with STORAGE and stainless steel appliances, seamlessly blends into a spacious living room, offering LAKE VIEWS and an atmosphere of FREEDOM. Enjoy those surreal lake views even more from the upgraded EXTENDED LANAI and included HOT TUB. First-floor TILE and GRANITE COUNTERTOPS keep things cool year-round. Upstairs, discover ample flex space—perfect for a studio, gaming room, or home theater. Additional ceiling STORAGE in the garage and a 2018 build minimizes INSURANCE, ROOF, AC, and WATER HEATER concerns. The property radiates CURB APPEAL with tasteful landscaping, built-in IRRIGATION, and a pavered driveway. Plus, activate the built-in pest service as needed, and consider adding a POOL or FENCE in the roomy backyard for your PETS!
